Completion of the program does not imply that an individual has the competence to perform neonatal resuscitation.

This Neonatal Resuscitation Program class uses an evidence-based approach to teach newborn resuscitation to health care professionals, including physicians, registered nurses, physician assistants and respiratory care practitioners, who have no previous experience.
